3. Klijent VALIDACIJA


# Foodbook

### API
Every route MUST include CSRF Token!! [ apiKey ]

Example:

```javascript
axios.get(`/users/read.php?apiKey=${token}`)
  .then(res => console.log(res.data)) // getting results
  .catch(err => console.log(err)) // catching error
```

### Plugins

Dillinger is currently extended with the following plugins. Instructions on how to use them in your own application are linked below.

### Users

| Method | Route | Explaination| Status Codes|
| ------ | ------ |------| ------|
| GET | /users/read.php | Get all users| 202|
| GET/:id | /users/read_single.php?id=:id | Get specific user by id | 202|
| POST | /users/create.php | Register user | 201|
| POST | /users/login.php | Login user with credentials | 202|
| PATCH/:id | /users/update.php?id=:id | Update specific user| 204|
